Text: Great collection as far as it goes. Where is the Synopticon and all the others?

i have uploaded all i have.!

sistromo -- apparently an uploader will upload what they have and not use a 'terrible' format just to yank downloaders chains ... so instead of whining and complaining about someone doing something you have not seen fit to do once on this tracker, convert the document into an 'acceptable' format (to you at least since i see no one else complaining) and then upload it so others may also share in your 'holier than thou' format ... 

until that time however, say thank you and stfu

long live pirates.
